1
00:00:23,875 --> 00:00:25,041
REPORT, MR. CHEKOV.

2
00:00:26,083 --> 00:00:27,834
FULL SCAN.

3
00:00:27,834 --> 00:00:29,834
RESULTS--NEGATIVE.

4
00:00:29,834 --> 00:00:31,500
RADIATION LEVEL--NORMAL.

5
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,542
ATMOSPHERE AND TERRAIN
ARE UNDISTURBED.

6
00:00:34,542 --> 00:00:35,875
NO EVIDENCE OF A COLONY

7
00:00:35,875 --> 00:00:38,041
NOR ANY RESIDUAL
AFTEREFFECT OF A FORCE

8
00:00:38,041 --> 00:00:40,166
THAT MIGHT HAVE
ANNIHILATED IT.

9
00:00:40,166 --> 00:00:41,291
LIFE READINGS, DR. McCOY?

10
00:00:41,291 --> 00:00:43,250
NOTHING. THEY SAID
THEY WERE
BEING ATTACKED

11
00:00:43,250 --> 00:00:45,000
BY AN UNIDENTIFIED SHIP.

12
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:47,500
WHICH WE WERE UNABLE TO
DETECT UPON APPROACH.

13
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:49,417
AN ENTIRE HUMAN COLONY.

14
00:00:51,959 --> 00:00:53,041
A WHOLE SETTLEMENT.

15
00:00:54,458 --> 00:00:56,500
100 MEN, WOMEN,
AND CHILDREN.

16
00:00:58,500 --> 00:01:00,291
WHO DID IT?

17
00:01:00,291 --> 00:01:01,917
AND WHY?

18
00:01:01,917 --> 00:01:04,041
[COMMUNICATOR BEEPS]

19
00:01:04,041 --> 00:01:05,041
KIRK HERE.

20
00:01:05,041 --> 00:01:06,166
SPOCK HERE, CAPTAIN.

21
00:01:06,166 --> 00:01:08,333
SENSORS HAVE PICKED UP
A KLINGON SHIP,

22
00:01:08,333 --> 00:01:09,583
CLOSING FAST.

23
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:12,583
DEFLECTORS ON.
CONDITION RED.

24
00:01:12,583 --> 00:01:13,959
PROTECT YOURSELVES.

25
00:01:13,959 --> 00:01:16,417
TOTAL REPLY
IF ATTACKED.

26
00:01:16,417 --> 00:01:17,917
SO THAT'S THE ANSWER--

27
00:01:17,917 --> 00:01:18,583
KLINGONS.

28
00:01:18,583 --> 00:01:20,291
TROUBLE ABOARD
THE KLINGON SHIP.

29
00:01:20,291 --> 00:01:22,125
EVIDENCE OF EXPLOSIONS,

30
00:01:22,125 --> 00:01:23,542
MASSIVE DESTRUCTION.

31
00:01:30,625 --> 00:01:34,083
CAPTAIN, THE ENEMY SHIP
IS DRIFTING,

32
00:01:34,083 --> 00:01:36,000
TOTALLY DISABLED,

33
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,959
AND WE NEVER FIRED
UPON HER.

34
00:01:37,959 --> 00:01:39,375
MAINTAIN RED ALERT.

35
00:01:39,375 --> 00:01:41,166
[FOOTSTEPS]

36
00:01:44,667 --> 00:01:47,834
YOU ATTACKED MY SHIP!

37
00:01:47,834 --> 00:01:51,125
400 OF MY CREW DEAD.

38
00:01:51,125 --> 00:01:53,875
KIRK, MY SHIP IS DISABLED.

39
00:01:53,875 --> 00:01:56,083
I CLAIM YOURS.

40
00:01:56,083 --> 00:01:58,166
YOU ARE NOW PRISONERS
OF THE KLINGON EMPIRE

41
00:01:58,166 --> 00:02:00,583
AGAINST WHICH YOU'VE COMMITTED
A WANTON ACT OF WAR!

42
00:02:15,959 --> 00:02:18,542
Kirk: SPACE--THE FINAL FRONTIER.

43
00:02:24,834 --> 00:02:29,083
THESE ARE THE VOYAGES
OF THE STARSHIP "ENTERPRISE."

44
00:02:29,083 --> 00:02:30,750
ITS 5-YEAR MISSION--

45
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:33,458
TO EXPLORE
STRANGE NEW WORLDS...

46
00:02:33,458 --> 00:02:37,458
TO SEEK OUT NEW LIFE
AND NEW CIVILIZATIONS...

47
00:02:37,458 --> 00:02:40,250
TO BOLDLY GO WHERE
NO MAN HAS GONE BEFORE.

48
00:03:25,375 --> 00:03:28,041
FOR 3 YEARS,
THE FEDERATION AND
THE KLINGON EMPIRE

49
00:03:28,041 --> 00:03:31,917
HAVE BEEN AT PEACE,

50
00:03:31,917 --> 00:03:34,000
A TREATY WE HAVE HONORED
TO THE LETTER.

51
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:37,458
WE TOOK NO ACTION
AGAINST YOUR SHIP, KANG.

52
00:03:37,458 --> 00:03:40,083
WERE THE SCREAMS
OF MY CREW IMAGINARY?

53
00:03:40,083 --> 00:03:41,625
WHAT WERE YOUR
ORDERS, KIRK?

54
00:03:41,625 --> 00:03:44,083
TO START A WAR?
YOU'VE SUCCEEDED.

55
00:03:44,083 --> 00:03:47,166
TO TEST A NEW WEAPON?
WE SHALL BE HAPPY
TO EXAMINE IT.

56
00:03:47,166 --> 00:03:48,834
THERE WAS A FEDERATION
COLONY ON THIS PLANET.

57
00:03:48,834 --> 00:03:49,834
IT WAS DESTROYED.

58
00:03:49,834 --> 00:03:51,250
BY WHAT?

59
00:03:51,250 --> 00:03:53,333
NO BODIES,
NO RUINS.

60
00:03:53,333 --> 00:03:56,208
A COLONY
OF THE INVISIBLE?

61
00:03:56,208 --> 00:03:58,959
YES, A TEST OF A NEW
KLINGON WEAPON,

62
00:03:58,959 --> 00:04:01,208
LEAVING NO TRACES.

63
00:04:01,208 --> 00:04:03,959
FEDERATION SHIPS
DON'T SPECIALIZE
IN SNEAK ATTACKS.

64
00:04:06,208 --> 00:04:09,083
WE HAVE WONDERED
WHEN YOU WOULD BEGIN.

65
00:04:09,083 --> 00:04:10,583
YOU LURED MY SHIP
INTO AMBUSH

66
00:04:10,583 --> 00:04:13,083
BY A FALSE KLINGON
DISTRESS CALL.

67
00:04:13,083 --> 00:04:15,125
YOU WILL TELL US WHY
WITH THE PROPER PERSUASION.

68
00:04:15,125 --> 00:04:16,500
YOU RECEIVED
A DISTRESS CALL?

69
00:04:16,500 --> 00:04:18,250
WE RECEIVED
A DISTRESS CALL.

70
00:04:18,250 --> 00:04:20,917
I DON'T PROPOSE TO SPEND
THE REST OF MY LIFE

71
00:04:20,917 --> 00:04:24,000
ON THIS BALL OF DUST,
ARGUING YOUR FANTASIES.

72
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,417
THE "ENTERPRISE" IS MINE!

73
00:04:28,041 --> 00:04:30,291
INSTRUCT YOUR TRANSPORTER
ROOM TO BEAM US ABOARD.

74
00:04:36,125 --> 00:04:37,458
GO TO THE DEVIL.

75
00:04:40,333 --> 00:04:42,417
WE HAVE NO DEVIL, KIRK.

76
00:04:45,083 --> 00:04:46,583
BUT WE UNDERSTAND
THE HABITS OF YOURS.

77
00:04:50,250 --> 00:04:53,125
I SHALL TORTURE YOU...

78
00:04:53,125 --> 00:04:55,041
TO DEATH...

79
00:04:55,041 --> 00:04:56,250
ONE BY ONE...

80
00:04:59,041 --> 00:05:01,041
UNTIL YOUR NOBLE CAPTAIN
CRIES "ENOUGH."

81
00:05:05,083 --> 00:05:06,625
WHO WILL BE FIRST?

82
00:05:17,875 --> 00:05:19,250
COSSACKS!

83
00:05:20,375 --> 00:05:23,417
FILTHY KLINGON MURDERERS!

84
00:05:23,417 --> 00:05:26,542
YOU KILLED
MY BROTHER PIOTRE.

85
00:05:26,542 --> 00:05:28,834
THE ARCANIS 4 RESEARCH
OUTPOST.

86
00:05:28,834 --> 00:05:31,041
100 PEACEFUL PEOPLE
MASSACRED!

87
00:05:32,083 --> 00:05:34,375
JUST LIKE YOU DID HERE.

88
00:05:34,375 --> 00:05:36,500
MY BROTHER--YOU KILLED HIM.

89
00:05:36,500 --> 00:05:38,083
AND YOU VOLUNTEER
TO JOIN HIM.

90
00:05:38,083 --> 00:05:39,125
THAT IS LOYALTY.

91
00:05:41,458 --> 00:05:43,917
AAH!

92
00:05:47,834 --> 00:05:48,792
CHEKOV!

93
00:05:53,250 --> 00:05:54,208
STOP THE TORTURE!

94
00:05:59,667 --> 00:06:02,792
JIM, YOU CAN'T HAND OVER
THE "ENTERPRISE."

95
00:06:02,792 --> 00:06:03,750
HELP CHEKOV.

96
00:06:06,667 --> 00:06:08,959
DON'T PLAN ANY TRICKS,
KIRK.

97
00:06:08,959 --> 00:06:11,208
I WILL KILL 100 HOSTAGES

98
00:06:11,208 --> 00:06:14,625
AT THE FIRST SIGN
OF TREACHERY.

99
00:06:14,625 --> 00:06:16,250
I'LL BEAM YOU ABOARD
THE "ENTERPRISE."

100
00:06:16,250 --> 00:06:17,917
ONCE THERE, NO TRICKS.

101
00:06:24,959 --> 00:06:27,375
Chekov: CAPTAIN,
YOU CAN'T.

102
00:06:27,375 --> 00:06:29,291
DON'T LET THESE ANIMALS
HAVE THE SHIP.

103
00:06:34,333 --> 00:06:36,083
MOVE ASIDE.

104
00:06:36,083 --> 00:06:38,208
Kang: ANIMALS?

105
00:06:38,208 --> 00:06:41,667
YOUR CAPTAIN
CRAWLS LIKE ONE.

106
00:06:41,667 --> 00:06:44,000
A KLINGON WOULD NEVER
HAVE SURRENDERED.

107
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:46,959
ORDER EVERYBODY IN THIS AREA
TO BE TRANSPORTED UP.

108
00:06:46,959 --> 00:06:48,000
ALL WEAPONS ON HIM.

109
00:06:54,917 --> 00:06:56,458
KIRK TO
"ENTERPRISE."

110
00:06:56,458 --> 00:06:57,917
MR. SPOCK.

111
00:06:57,917 --> 00:07:00,125
HERE, CAPTAIN.

112
00:07:00,125 --> 00:07:02,458
MR. SPOCK,
WE HAVE GUESTS.

113
00:07:02,458 --> 00:07:04,458
ADJUST TRANSPORTER
TO WIDE FIELD.

114
00:07:04,458 --> 00:07:07,417
BEAM UP EVERYONE
IN THE TARGET AREA.

115
00:07:16,500 --> 00:07:17,792
UNDERSTOOD, CAPTAIN.

116
00:07:19,250 --> 00:07:20,375
TRANSPORTER ROOM.

117
00:07:40,709 --> 00:07:43,125
FULL SECURITY, JOHNSON,
ON THE DOUBLE.

118
00:07:43,125 --> 00:07:44,125
GOOD WORK, SPOCK.

119
00:07:44,125 --> 00:07:45,083
WHAT HAPPENED?

120
00:07:45,083 --> 00:07:46,709
OUR LANDING PARTY
IS INTACT, DOCTOR.

121
00:07:46,709 --> 00:07:48,625
ALL OTHERS SUSPENDED
IN TRANSIT.

122
00:07:48,625 --> 00:07:50,125
WHO ARE THE GUESTS,
BY THE WAY?

123
00:07:50,125 --> 00:07:51,291
KLINGONS.

124
00:07:51,291 --> 00:07:53,375
WELL, THEY'RE RIGHT
IN HERE.

125
00:07:53,375 --> 00:07:54,375
JOHNSON?

126
00:07:54,375 --> 00:07:55,834
SECURITY ON THE WAY, SIR.

127
00:07:55,834 --> 00:07:58,000
CAPTAIN, LEAVE THEM
WHERE THEY ARE--

128
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,583
NONEXISTENCE.

129
00:07:59,583 --> 00:08:01,625
THAT'S SO MANY LESS
KLINGON MONSTERS
IN THE GALAXY.

130
00:08:05,959 --> 00:08:06,917
BRING THEM IN.

131
00:08:18,333 --> 00:08:19,542
MOVE 'EM OUT. MOVE!

132
00:08:22,166 --> 00:08:23,583
LIAR!

133
00:08:23,583 --> 00:08:27,083
I SAID NO TRICKS AFTER
WE REACH THE SHIP.

134
00:08:27,083 --> 00:08:28,834
YOU'RE A PRISONER
OF THE FEDERATION OF PLANETS

135
00:08:28,834 --> 00:08:30,792
AGAINST WHICH YOU MAY
OR MAY NOT

136
00:08:30,792 --> 00:08:32,583
HAVE COMMITTED
AN ACT OF WAR.

137
00:08:32,583 --> 00:08:35,000
THERE ARE STILL
SURVIVORS ABOARD
MY SHIP.

138
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:37,750
CAPTAIN, WE'VE NOT BEEN
ABLE TO GET THROUGH
TO STARFLEET COMMAND.

139
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:40,125
ALL SUBSPACE FREQUENCIES
HAVE BEEN BLOCKED,

140
00:08:40,125 --> 00:08:43,375
AND THERE'S TOO MUCH RADIATION
COMING FROM THAT KLINGON SHIP.

141
00:08:43,375 --> 00:08:44,625
IT'S A HAZARD
TO THE VICINITY.

142
00:08:44,625 --> 00:08:46,417
PREPARE TO DESTRUCT.

143
00:08:46,417 --> 00:08:48,667
COMPLETING THE JOB
YOU STARTED?

144
00:08:48,667 --> 00:08:50,667
YOU WOULDN'T BE STANDING
HERE IF I HAD.

145
00:08:50,667 --> 00:08:52,458
FIRST GROUP FROM
THE KLINGON VESSEL,
CAPTAIN.

146
00:09:01,333 --> 00:09:04,333
MY WIFE MARA
AND MY SCIENCE OFFICER.

147
00:09:06,333 --> 00:09:08,166
KANG, WHAT HAS HAPPENED?

148
00:09:08,166 --> 00:09:10,417
MORE FEDERATION
TREACHERY.

149
00:09:10,417 --> 00:09:12,875
WE ARE PRISONERS.

150
00:09:12,875 --> 00:09:15,166
WHAT WILL THEY DO TO US?

151
00:09:15,166 --> 00:09:19,333
I'VE HEARD OF
THEIR ATROCITIES,
THEIR DEATH CAMPS.

152
00:09:19,333 --> 00:09:22,792
THEY WILL TORTURE US
FOR OUR SCIENTIFIC AND
MILITARY INFORMATION.

153
00:09:22,792 --> 00:09:24,500
APPARENTLY YOU HAVE
A FEW THINGS
TO LEARN ABOUT US.

154
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:26,458
DETAIN THEM
IN THE CREW LOUNGE.

155
00:09:26,458 --> 00:09:28,125
PROGRAM
THE FOOD SYNTHESIZER

156
00:09:28,125 --> 00:09:29,458
TO ACCOMMODATE
OUR GUESTS.

157
00:09:29,458 --> 00:09:31,333
YOU'LL BE WELL-TREATED,
KANG.

158
00:09:31,333 --> 00:09:32,333
SO I HAVE SEEN.

159
00:09:38,250 --> 00:09:39,500
SECURE FROM RED ALERT.

160
00:09:42,333 --> 00:09:44,000
BUT MAINTAIN
GENERAL QUARTERS.

161
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,458
SCAN THIS SECTOR
FOR OTHER SHIPS.

162
00:09:45,458 --> 00:09:46,583
RUN A FULL CHECK
ON THE COLONY.

163
00:09:46,583 --> 00:09:48,417
I WANT THIS THING
NAILED DOWN FAST.

164
00:09:48,417 --> 00:09:51,083
WE KNOW WHAT HAPPENED.
THAT DISTRESS CALL.

165
00:09:51,083 --> 00:09:53,208
AT THE MOMENT
WE RECEIVED
THE DISTRESS SIGNAL

166
00:09:53,208 --> 00:09:55,417
FROM THE COLONY
ON BETA 12-A,

167
00:09:55,417 --> 00:09:56,917
THE KLINGONS WERE
TOO FAR DISTANT

168
00:09:56,917 --> 00:09:59,333
TO HAVE BEEN
THE ATTACKERS.

169
00:09:59,333 --> 00:10:01,792
MOREOVER, THEY ALSO WERE
APPARENTLY ATTRACTED

170
00:10:01,792 --> 00:10:03,208
BY A DISTRESS CALL.

171
00:10:07,834 --> 00:10:09,750
LIES. THEY WANT
TO START A WAR

172
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:11,333
BY PRETENDING
THAT WE DID.

173
00:10:11,333 --> 00:10:13,417
CHEKOV MAY BE RIGHT.

174
00:10:13,417 --> 00:10:15,458
THE KLINGONS CLAIM
TO HAVE HONORED
THE TRUCE,

175
00:10:15,458 --> 00:10:16,208
BUT THERE HAVE
BEEN INCIDENTS,

176
00:10:16,208 --> 00:10:17,792
RAIDS ON
OUR OUTPOSTS.

177
00:10:17,792 --> 00:10:19,667
NO PROOF THAT
THE KLINGONS
COMMITTED IT.

178
00:10:19,667 --> 00:10:21,417
WHAT PROOF
DO WE NEED?

179
00:10:21,417 --> 00:10:23,333
WE KNOW
WHAT A KLINGON IS.

180
00:10:31,417 --> 00:10:33,750
OUR LOG TAPES WILL
INDICATE OUR INNOCENCE

181
00:10:33,750 --> 00:10:34,959
IN THE PRESENT SITUATION.

182
00:10:34,959 --> 00:10:36,625
UNFORTUNATELY,
THERE'S NO GUARANTEE

183
00:10:36,625 --> 00:10:37,709
THAT THEY WILL
BE BELIEVED.

184
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:45,417
REPORT.

185
00:10:45,417 --> 00:10:47,542
STILL NO CONTACT WITH
STARFLEET COMMAND, SIR.

186
00:10:47,542 --> 00:10:49,041
OUTSIDE COMMUNICATIONS
BLANKETED.

187
00:10:49,041 --> 00:10:51,500
KEEP TRYING. WE'VE GOT
A DIPLOMATIC TIGER
BY THE TAIL.

188
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:53,083
Scotty:
TRANSPORTER ROOM
TO BRIDGE.

189
00:10:53,083 --> 00:10:54,542
KLINGON SHIP
IS VACATED, SIR.

190
00:10:54,542 --> 00:10:56,583
VERY GOOD, SCOTTY.
MR. SULU?

191
00:10:56,583 --> 00:10:58,166
FORWARD PHASERS
LOCKED AND READY
TO FIRE, SIR.

192
00:10:58,166 --> 00:10:59,125
FIRE PHASERS.

193
00:11:07,041 --> 00:11:10,417
SENSOR SWEEPS
REVEAL NO OTHER SHIPS
WITHIN RANGE, CAPTAIN.

194
00:11:10,417 --> 00:11:11,500
LIEUTENANT UHURA?

195
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:13,792
NO CONTACT
WITH STARFLEET
AS YET, SIR.

196
00:11:13,792 --> 00:11:15,959
MR. SULU, CHANGE COURSE
TO 17 MARK 4,

197
00:11:15,959 --> 00:11:17,125
WARP FACTOR 3.

198
00:11:17,125 --> 00:11:18,375
WARP FACTOR 3, SIR.

199
00:11:41,583 --> 00:11:43,458
WHEN I TAKE THIS SHIP,

200
00:11:43,458 --> 00:11:46,709
I'LL HAVE KIRK'S HEAD
STUFFED AND HUNG
ON HIS CABIN WALL.

201
00:11:46,709 --> 00:11:48,166
THEY WILL KILL US
BEFORE WE CAN ACT.

202
00:11:48,166 --> 00:11:50,375
NO, THEY WISH
TO QUESTION US,

203
00:11:50,375 --> 00:11:52,875
LEARN OUR STRENGTH,
OUR PLANS.

204
00:11:52,875 --> 00:11:54,291
THEY NEVER WILL.

205
00:11:54,291 --> 00:11:57,709
WE ARE 40 AGAINST 400.

206
00:11:57,709 --> 00:12:00,834
4,000 THROATS
MAY BE CUT
IN ONE NIGHT

207
00:12:00,834 --> 00:12:02,250
BY
A RUNNING MAN.

208
00:12:02,250 --> 00:12:05,458
PATIENCE. VIGILANCE.

209
00:12:05,458 --> 00:12:07,834
THEY WILL MAKE
THEIR MISTAKE.

210
00:12:07,834 --> 00:12:09,834
CAPTURE OF THE "ENTERPRISE"
WILL GIVE US KNOWLEDGE

211
00:12:09,834 --> 00:12:11,542
TO END THIS WAR QUICKLY.

212
00:12:20,583 --> 00:12:21,542
CAPTAIN!

213
00:12:25,458 --> 00:12:27,709
THIS DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

214
00:12:27,709 --> 00:12:30,250
CARRIERS ARE NORMAL.
CHANNELS ARE OPEN.

215
00:12:30,250 --> 00:12:31,709
THERE'S STILL NO
OUTSIDE CONTACT!

216
00:12:31,709 --> 00:12:33,041
I DON'T
UNDERSTAND IT, SIR.

217
00:12:33,041 --> 00:12:34,500
COULD THE KLINGONS
BE DOING SOMETHING?

218
00:12:43,834 --> 00:12:45,041
SULU?

219
00:12:45,041 --> 00:12:48,166
CHANGE IN COURSE,
ACCELERATING.

220
00:12:48,166 --> 00:12:49,375
HELM DEAD.

221
00:12:51,333 --> 00:12:53,375
AUXILIARY NAVIGATION
DEAD.

222
00:12:53,375 --> 00:12:54,333
OVERRIDE.

223
00:12:56,333 --> 00:12:57,500
NOTHING RESPONDS,
CAPTAIN.

224
00:13:07,625 --> 00:13:09,667
SCOTTY, STOP ALL ENGINES.

225
00:13:09,667 --> 00:13:11,500
I WOULD IF I COULD, SIR,

226
00:13:11,500 --> 00:13:14,333
BUT THE CONTROLS
HAVE GONE CRAZY.

227
00:13:14,333 --> 00:13:16,458
SOMETHING'S TAKEN OVER.

228
00:13:16,458 --> 00:13:17,667
SCOTTY!

229
00:13:17,667 --> 00:13:20,166
THE ENGINES, SIR.
THEY'VE GONE TO WARP 9

230
00:13:20,166 --> 00:13:22,542
BY THEMSELVES!

231
00:13:22,542 --> 00:13:23,875
NEW COURSE?

232
00:13:23,875 --> 00:13:26,500
Sulu:
9-0-2, MARK 5.

233
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:27,792
THAT'LL TAKE US
OUT OF THE GALAXY.

234
00:13:36,542 --> 00:13:38,333
CAPTAIN, REPORTS COMING IN
FROM THE LOWER DECKS.

235
00:13:38,333 --> 00:13:40,667
EMERGENCY BULKHEADS
HAVE CLOSED.

236
00:13:40,667 --> 00:13:42,625
ALMOST 400 CREWMEN ARE
TRAPPED DOWN THERE, SIR.

237
00:13:50,875 --> 00:13:53,667
MOST INTERESTING.

