MAY I SAY THAT I HAVE
NOT THOROUGHLY ENJOYED
SERVING WITH HUMANS?

473
00:26:26,166 --> 00:26:29,083
I FIND THEIR ILLOGIC
AND FOOLISH EMOTIONS

474
00:26:29,083 --> 00:26:30,458
A CONSTANT IRRITANT.

475
00:26:30,458 --> 00:26:32,792
THEN TRANSFER OUT! FREAK!

476
00:26:37,959 --> 00:26:38,917
GENTLEMEN!

477
00:26:40,834 --> 00:26:41,834
SPOCK!

478
00:26:41,834 --> 00:26:43,083
SCOTTY.

479
00:26:43,083 --> 00:26:44,834
SPOCK. SPOCK!

480
00:26:46,792 --> 00:26:48,333
STOP IT!
YOU'RE HALF HUMAN!

481
00:26:55,083 --> 00:26:57,291
WHAT ARE WE SAYING?

482
00:26:57,291 --> 00:27:00,917
WHAT ARE WE DOING
TO EACH OTHER?

483
00:27:00,917 --> 00:27:03,291
FASCINATING.

484
00:27:03,291 --> 00:27:05,333
A RESULT OF STRESS?

485
00:27:05,333 --> 00:27:06,625
WE'VE BEEN UNDER
STRESS BEFORE.

486
00:27:06,625 --> 00:27:07,583
IT'S NEVER SET US

487
00:27:07,583 --> 00:27:09,333
AT EACH OTHER'S
THROATS.

488
00:27:09,333 --> 00:27:11,166
BUT THIS IS WAR.

489
00:27:11,166 --> 00:27:12,291
THERE ISN'T
ANY WAR!

490
00:27:16,208 --> 00:27:17,834
OR IS THERE?

491
00:27:17,834 --> 00:27:19,667
HAVE WE FORGOTTEN
HOW TO DEFEND OURSELVES?

492
00:27:19,667 --> 00:27:21,625
SCOTTY.

493
00:27:21,625 --> 00:27:24,166
WHAT'S HAPPENING
TO US?

494
00:27:24,166 --> 00:27:25,959
WE'VE BEEN
TRAINED TO THINK

495
00:27:25,959 --> 00:27:29,125
IN OTHER TERMS
THAN WAR.

496
00:27:29,125 --> 00:27:33,041
WE'VE BEEN TRAINED
TO FIGHT ITS CAUSES,
IF NECESSARY.

497
00:27:33,041 --> 00:27:34,041
THEN WHY ARE
WE BEHAVING

498
00:27:34,041 --> 00:27:37,333
LIKE A GROUP
OF SAVAGES?

499
00:27:37,333 --> 00:27:40,000
LOOK AT ME.

500
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:41,500
LOOK AT ME.

501
00:27:48,333 --> 00:27:51,917
TWO FORCES
ABOARD THIS SHIP,

502
00:27:51,917 --> 00:27:53,458
EACH OF THEM
EQUALLY ARMED.

503
00:27:55,959 --> 00:28:00,458
HAS A WAR BEEN
STAGED FOR US,

504
00:28:00,458 --> 00:28:03,583
COMPLETE
WITH WEAPONS

505
00:28:03,583 --> 00:28:05,417
AND IDEOLOGY

506
00:28:05,417 --> 00:28:08,291
AND PATRIOTIC
DRUM-BEATING?

507
00:28:08,291 --> 00:28:09,500
EVEN...

508
00:28:10,291 --> 00:28:11,500
SPOCK.

509
00:28:13,125 --> 00:28:14,333
EVEN...

510
00:28:16,125 --> 00:28:17,125
RACE HATRED?

511
00:28:18,750 --> 00:28:20,458
RECENT EVENTS WOULD
SEEM TO BE DIRECTED

512
00:28:20,458 --> 00:28:23,542
TOWARD A MAGNIFICATION
OF THE BASIC HOSTILITIES

513
00:28:23,542 --> 00:28:26,125
BETWEEN HUMANS
AND KLINGONS.

514
00:28:26,125 --> 00:28:29,333
APPARENTLY, IT IS BY DESIGN
THAT WE FIGHT.

515
00:28:30,959 --> 00:28:32,291
WE SEEM TO BE PAWNS.

516
00:28:32,291 --> 00:28:34,792
BUT WHAT'S THE GAME?

517
00:28:34,792 --> 00:28:36,417
AND WHOSE?

518
00:28:36,417 --> 00:28:38,250
AND WHAT ARE
THE RULES?

519
00:28:38,250 --> 00:28:40,291
IT IS MOST URGENT

520
00:28:40,291 --> 00:28:43,291
THAT WE LOCATE
THE ALIEN ENTITY IMMEDIATELY

521
00:28:43,291 --> 00:28:44,750
AND DETERMINE ITS MOTIVES

522
00:28:44,750 --> 00:28:47,000
AND A METHOD FOR HALTING
ITS ACTIVITIES.

523
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:49,125
WITHOUT SENSORS?

524
00:28:49,125 --> 00:28:50,625
ALL OUR POWER DOWN?

525
00:28:50,625 --> 00:28:52,875
THIS THING
COULD GO ANYWHERE.

526
00:28:52,875 --> 00:28:54,083
YES.

527
00:28:59,875 --> 00:29:01,125
MR. SULU, REPORT.

528
00:29:01,125 --> 00:29:03,333
NO GOOD, CAPTAIN.
CIRCUITS ARE IN,

529
00:29:03,333 --> 00:29:05,250
BUT SYSTEMS JUST
AREN'T RESPONDING.

530
00:29:08,333 --> 00:29:09,458
WE'RE GETTING SOMETHING.

531
00:29:11,375 --> 00:29:13,500
AYE, CAPTAIN.

532
00:29:13,500 --> 00:29:15,792
POWER AND LIFE-SUPPORT
RESTORED.

533
00:29:17,125 --> 00:29:18,792
REMOTE'S ON STANDBY.

534
00:29:18,792 --> 00:29:19,667
GOOD WORK.

535
00:29:19,667 --> 00:29:22,417
BUT, CAPTAIN,
I DIDN'T DO IT.

536
00:29:22,417 --> 00:29:24,417
EVERYTHING JUST
CAME ON BY ITSELF.

537
00:29:29,583 --> 00:29:33,041
THEIR LIFE-SUPPORT SYSTEMS
HAVE RESUMED.

538
00:29:33,041 --> 00:29:34,125
SENSORS MAY BE OPERATING.

539
00:29:34,125 --> 00:29:35,917
START SCANNING.

540
00:29:35,917 --> 00:29:37,250
LET'S FIND THAT ALIEN.

541
00:29:39,625 --> 00:29:40,917
HOLDING STEADY.

542
00:29:40,917 --> 00:29:42,166
CAUSE THEM
TO BE UNSTEADY.

543
00:29:48,291 --> 00:29:49,709
THEY APPEAR
TO BE CONTROLLED

544
00:29:49,709 --> 00:29:51,208
FROM ANOTHER LOCATION.

545
00:29:53,208 --> 00:29:55,166
ALSO UNABLE TO AFFECT
SHIP'S COURSE

546
00:29:55,166 --> 00:29:56,667
FOR RETURN
TO OUR EMPIRE.

547
00:29:58,125 --> 00:29:59,417
ONE OF KIRK'S TRICKS.

548
00:30:01,709 --> 00:30:03,959
COULD HE BYPASS
THIS CIRCUIT?

549
00:30:05,959 --> 00:30:08,667
WHAT POWER IS IT THAT
SUPPORTS OUR BATTLE

550
00:30:08,667 --> 00:30:10,000
YET STARVES OUR VICTORY?

551
00:30:11,500 --> 00:30:15,709
POWER. INTERRUPT IT
AT THEIR MAIN

552
00:30:15,709 --> 00:30:17,583
LIFE-SUPPORT COUPLINGS.

553
00:30:17,583 --> 00:30:18,750
WHERE?

554
00:30:18,750 --> 00:30:20,083
NUMBER 6 DECK.

555
00:30:21,917 --> 00:30:22,875
COME.

556
00:30:40,625 --> 00:30:42,166
ALIEN DETECTED

557
00:30:42,166 --> 00:30:43,333
IN THE ENGINEERING SECTION,

558
00:30:43,333 --> 00:30:45,709
NEAR REACTOR NUMBER 3.

559
00:30:47,291 --> 00:30:48,333
LET'S GO.

560
00:31:50,166 --> 00:31:52,750
YOU DON'T DIE YET.

561
00:31:56,125 --> 00:31:57,291
YOU'RE NOT HUMAN...

562
00:31:59,417 --> 00:32:01,083
BUT YOU'RE VERY BEAUTIFUL.

563
00:32:02,583 --> 00:32:04,875
VERY...

564
00:32:04,875 --> 00:32:05,917
BEAUTIFUL.

565
00:32:23,834 --> 00:32:25,041
CHEKOV!

566
00:32:29,709 --> 00:32:31,917
JIM, HE'S NOT RESPONSIBLE.

567
00:32:38,125 --> 00:32:39,375
WHAT HAVE I DONE?

568
00:32:51,333 --> 00:32:54,625
THERE'S A-AN ALIEN ENTITY
ABOARD THE SHIP.

569
00:32:54,625 --> 00:32:56,458
IT'S FORCING US TO FIGHT.
WE DON'T WANT TO.

570
00:32:56,458 --> 00:32:58,750
WE DON'T KNOW WHAT
ITS MOTIVE IS.

571
00:32:58,750 --> 00:33:01,583
WE'RE TRYING TO FIND OUT.
YOU MUST HELP US.

572
00:33:01,583 --> 00:33:02,834
TAKE ME TO KANG.

573
00:33:02,834 --> 00:33:04,542
A TEMPORARY TRUCE,
THAT'S ALL I ASK.

574
00:33:10,041 --> 00:33:11,917
SPOCK, TAKE HER.

575
00:33:15,959 --> 00:33:16,917
CHEKOV.

576
00:33:18,208 --> 00:33:19,542
CHEKOV.

577
00:33:22,542 --> 00:33:25,875
IS THIS WHAT'S
IN STORE FOR US,

578
00:33:25,875 --> 00:33:28,083
FROM HERE ON IN?

579
00:33:28,083 --> 00:33:29,917
VIOLENCE,

580
00:33:29,917 --> 00:33:30,875
HATRED.

581
00:33:49,041 --> 00:33:51,125
BRAIN WAVES SHOW
ALMOST PARANOID MANIA.

582
00:33:51,125 --> 00:33:52,792
WHAT HAPPENED?

583
00:33:52,792 --> 00:33:54,875
HE LOST CONTROL.

584
00:33:54,875 --> 00:33:56,917
SO DID I.

585
00:33:56,917 --> 00:34:01,083
WE'RE BECOMING
ANIMAL WARRIORS.

586
00:34:01,083 --> 00:34:02,125
LET'S GO, SPOCK.

587
00:34:02,125 --> 00:34:03,750
ORDERLY.

588
00:34:03,750 --> 00:34:04,709
JIM.

589
00:34:09,208 --> 00:34:10,291
JOHNSON'S
HEART WOUND

590
00:34:10,291 --> 00:34:11,542
IS ALMOST
COMPLETELY HEALED.

591
00:34:11,542 --> 00:34:13,250
THE SAME
WITH THE OTHER
CASUALTIES.

592
00:34:13,250 --> 00:34:15,041
SWORD WOUNDS
IN THE VITAL ORGANS,

593
00:34:15,041 --> 00:34:16,917
MASSIVE TRAUMA,
SHOCK--

594
00:34:16,917 --> 00:34:19,458
THEY'RE ALL HEALING
AT A FANTASTIC RATE.

595
00:34:19,458 --> 00:34:22,291
IT WOULD APPEAR
THAT THE ENTITY
WANTS US ALIVE.

596
00:34:22,291 --> 00:34:24,834
WHY? SO WE CAN FIGHT

597
00:34:24,834 --> 00:34:26,834
AND FIGHT AND KEEP
COMING BACK FOR MORE

598
00:34:26,834 --> 00:34:29,208
LIKE SOME BLOODY COLISEUM?

599
00:34:29,208 --> 00:34:31,166
WHAT'S NEXT,
THE ROAR OF CROWDS?

600
00:34:31,166 --> 00:34:34,709
PERHAPS HUMAN AND KLINGON
PSYCHOLOGIES

601
00:34:34,709 --> 00:34:37,750
AND COMBAT CAPABILITIES
ARE BEING TESTED

602
00:34:37,750 --> 00:34:40,917
BY AN ALIEN WITH DESIGNS
ON BOTH POWERS.

603
00:34:40,917 --> 00:34:42,834
GENTLEMEN,
IF WE ARE PAWNS,

604
00:34:42,834 --> 00:34:46,208
YOU'RE LOOKING
AT ONE WHO IS
EXTREMELY SORRY.

605
00:34:46,208 --> 00:34:48,041
I UNDERSTAND, DOCTOR.

606
00:34:48,041 --> 00:34:51,417
I, TOO, FELT A BRIEF SURGE
OF RACIAL BIGOTRY.

607
00:34:51,417 --> 00:34:54,083
MOST DISTASTEFUL.

608
00:34:54,083 --> 00:34:56,125
LET'S FIND THE ALIEN.

609
00:34:57,166 --> 00:34:59,667
YOU COME WITH US.

610
00:34:59,667 --> 00:35:01,667
MAYBE WE CAN PROVE TO YOU
THAT IT EXISTS.

611
00:35:28,500 --> 00:35:30,417
WHAT IS IT?

612
00:35:30,417 --> 00:35:31,667
TOTALLY UNFAMILIAR.

613
00:35:39,166 --> 00:35:40,375
WHAT IS IT YOU WANT?

614
00:35:42,375 --> 00:35:43,458
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

615
00:35:46,166 --> 00:35:47,500
REPORTING FOR DUTY, SIR.

616
00:35:49,834 --> 00:35:52,834
DUTY? DID McCOY RELEASE
YOU FROM SICK BAY?

617
00:35:52,834 --> 00:35:53,792
I RELEASED MYSELF.

618
00:35:53,792 --> 00:35:55,083
THEN GET BACK
TO SICK BAY!

619
00:35:55,083 --> 00:35:58,250
NOT ON YOUR LIFE, SIR.
I'M FIT AND READY
FOR ACTION.

620
00:35:58,250 --> 00:35:59,291
KLINGONS ALMOST
DID ME IN ONCE.

621
00:35:59,291 --> 00:36:00,709
I'M OUT
TO EVEN THE SCORE.

622
00:36:00,709 --> 00:36:01,625
I ORDER YOU--

623
00:36:01,625 --> 00:36:02,625
I'VE GOT MY ORDERS.

624
00:36:02,625 --> 00:36:05,000
I'M OBEYING ORDERS!
KILL THE KLINGONS!

625
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:06,500
IT'S THEM OR US,
ISN'T IT?

626
00:36:06,500 --> 00:36:07,834
JOHNSON!

627
00:36:07,834 --> 00:36:09,250
UH!

628
00:36:18,041 --> 00:36:20,375
FASCINATING.

629
00:36:20,375 --> 00:36:21,458
DURING
LIEUTENANT JOHNSON'S

630
00:36:21,458 --> 00:36:22,875
EMOTIONAL OUTBURST,

631
00:36:22,875 --> 00:36:26,250
HIS EXPRESSION
OF HATRED AND LUST
FOR VENGEANCE,

632
00:36:26,250 --> 00:36:29,875
THE ALIEN'S
LIFE ENERGY LEVEL
INCREASED.

633
00:36:29,875 --> 00:36:32,375
WHEN THE LIEUTENANT
BECAME UNCONSCIOUS,

634
00:36:32,375 --> 00:36:34,750
THE ALIEN
LOST ENERGY.

635
00:36:34,750 --> 00:36:36,417
IT SUBSISTS

636
00:36:36,417 --> 00:36:38,792
ON THE EMOTIONS OF OTHERS.

637
00:36:38,792 --> 00:36:41,417
THIS ONE APPEARS
TO BE STRENGTHENED

638
00:36:41,417 --> 00:36:44,500
BY MENTAL RADIATIONS
OF HOSTILITY,

639
00:36:44,500 --> 00:36:46,041
VIOLENT INTENTIONS.

640
00:36:48,333 --> 00:36:53,458
IT EXISTS ON THE HATE
OF OTHERS.

641
00:36:53,458 --> 00:36:55,500
TO PUT IT SIMPLY.

642
00:36:55,500 --> 00:36:57,375
AND IT HAS ACTED
AS A CATALYST,

643
00:36:57,375 --> 00:36:59,417
CREATING
THIS SITUATION

644
00:36:59,417 --> 00:37:01,542
IN ORDER TO SATISFY
THAT NEED.

645
00:37:01,542 --> 00:37:03,834
IT HAS BROUGHT
TOGETHER
OPPOSING FORCES,

646
00:37:03,834 --> 00:37:06,291
PROVIDED
CRUDE INSTRUMENTS

647
00:37:06,291 --> 00:37:07,583
IN AN EFFORT
TO PROMOTE

648
00:37:07,583 --> 00:37:10,750
THE MOST VIOLENT
MODE OF CONFLICT.

649
00:37:10,750 --> 00:37:14,583
AND KEPT NUMBERS
AND RESOURCES BALANCED

650
00:37:14,583 --> 00:37:16,667
SO THAT IT CAN MAINTAIN

651
00:37:16,667 --> 00:37:18,875
A CONSTANT STATE
OF VIOLENCE.

652
00:37:18,875 --> 00:37:22,917
IT'S GOT TO HAVE
A VULNERABLE AREA.

653
00:37:22,917 --> 00:37:24,500
WE'VE GOT TO GET RID OF IT.

654
00:37:24,500 --> 00:37:26,875
THEN ALL HOSTILE
ATTITUDES ON BOARD

655
00:37:26,875 --> 00:37:28,500
MUST BE ELIMINATED.

656
00:37:28,500 --> 00:37:30,959
THE FIGHTING
MUST END AND SOON.

657
00:37:30,959 --> 00:37:33,125
OR WE'RE A DOOMED SHIP,

658
00:37:33,125 --> 00:37:34,917
TRAVELING FOREVER
BETWEEN GALAXIES,

659
00:37:34,917 --> 00:37:37,166
FILLED WITH ETERNAL
BLOOD LUST,

660
00:37:37,166 --> 00:37:38,417
ETERNAL WARFARE.

661
00:37:40,375 --> 00:37:42,917
KANG HAS GOT TO LISTEN.

662
00:37:42,917 --> 00:37:45,291
WE'VE GOT TO POOL
OUR KNOWLEDGE

663
00:37:45,291 --> 00:37:47,291
AND GET RID OF THIS THING.

664
00:38:00,625 --> 00:38:03,250
KANG.

665
00:38:03,250 --> 00:38:06,333
KANG, THIS IS
CAPTAIN KIRK.

666
00:38:06,333 --> 00:38:08,250
KANG, DO YOU READ ME?

667
00:38:08,250 --> 00:38:10,041
COMMANDER!
IT'S A TRICK!

668
00:38:16,959 --> 00:38:18,166
KANG.

669
00:38:22,125 --> 00:38:24,542
HE WON'T ANSWER.

670
00:38:24,542 --> 00:38:27,125
THE ALIEN IS AFFECTING
HIS MIND, CAPTAIN.

671
00:38:27,125 --> 00:38:29,000
SOON IT WILL BECOME
SO POWERFUL

672
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:31,917
THAT NONE OF US WILL BE
ABLE TO RESIST IT.

673
00:38:31,917 --> 00:38:34,083
[INTERCOM SIGNAL]

674
00:38:34,083 --> 00:38:35,250
SCOTTY, SIR.

675
00:38:35,250 --> 00:38:37,375
THE SHIP'S DILITHIUM CRYSTALS
ARE DETERIORATING.

676
00:38:37,375 --> 00:38:39,417
WE CAN'T STOP THE PROCESS.

677
00:38:39,417 --> 00:38:40,667
TIME FACTOR?

678
00:38:40,667 --> 00:38:41,583
IN 12 MINUTES,

679
00:38:41,583 --> 00:38:43,583
WE'LL BE TOTALLY
WITHOUT ENGINE POWER.

680
00:38:45,834 --> 00:38:48,583
WELL...

681
00:38:48,583 --> 00:38:50,375
DO WHATEVER YOU CAN.
KIRK OUT.

682
00:39:05,417 --> 00:39:08,458
AND SO WE DRIFT
IN SPACE

683
00:39:08,458 --> 00:39:09,542
WITH ONLY HATRED

684
00:39:09,542 --> 00:39:11,083
AND BLOODSHED
ABOARD.

685
00:39:14,291 --> 00:39:15,583
NOW DO YOU
BELIEVE?

686
00:39:24,208 --> 00:39:27,000
Kirk: CAPTAIN'S LOG, STARDATE...

687
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:29,083
ARMAGEDDON.

688
00:39:29,083 --> 00:39:30,458
WE MUST FIND A WAY

689
00:39:30,458 --> 00:39:32,500
TO DEFEAT
THE ALIEN FORCE OF HATE

690
00:39:32,500 --> 00:39:34,250
THAT HAS TAKEN OVER
THE ENTERPRISE,

691
00:39:34,250 --> 00:39:36,834
STOP THE WAR NOW,

692
00:39:36,834 --> 00:39:41,583
OR SPEND ETERNITY
IN FUTILE BLOODY VIOLENCE.

693
00:39:41,583 --> 00:39:43,041
THERE'S NO CHANGE,
CAPTAIN.

694
00:39:43,041 --> 00:39:45,583
THE DILITHIUM
CRYSTALS ARE
DISCHARGING.

695
00:39:45,583 --> 00:39:47,500
THERE'S NOTHING
WE CAN DO ABOUT IT.

696
00:39:47,500 --> 00:39:49,709
IF I COULD TALK TO KANG...

697
00:39:49,709 --> 00:39:52,166
SOMEHOW CUT THROUGH
THE KLINGON LINES,

698
00:39:52,166 --> 00:39:54,166
MAKE PEACE BEFORE
IT'S TOO LATE.

699
00:39:54,166 --> 00:39:57,333
WE HAVE 9 MINUTES,
53 SECONDS TO POWER ZERO.

700
00:39:57,333 --> 00:40:00,500
THERE IS, OF COURSE,
A LOGICAL ALTERNATIVE.

701
00:40:00,500 --> 00:40:03,125
KANG'S WIFE IS, AFTER ALL,
OUR PRISONER.

702
00:40:03,125 --> 00:40:04,875
PERHAPS A THREAT.

703
00:40:04,875 --> 00:40:06,333
AYE.

704
00:40:06,333 --> 00:40:08,959
NOW THAT'S SOMETHING
THE KLINGONS
WOULD UNDERSTAND.

705
00:40:21,875 --> 00:40:22,875
[CLICKS ON INTERCOM]

706
00:40:22,875 --> 00:40:25,083
KANG.

707
00:40:25,083 --> 00:40:26,834
KANG, THIS IS
CAPTAIN KIRK.

708
00:40:26,834 --> 00:40:30,041
I KNOW YOU CAN HEAR ME,
SO DON'T CUT ME OFF.

709
00:40:30,041 --> 00:40:33,208
WE HAVE MARA, YOUR WIFE.

710
00:40:33,208 --> 00:40:36,000
WE TALK TRUCE NOW,

711
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:37,458
OR SHE DIES. REPLY.

712
00:40:41,291 --> 00:40:43,917
SHE HAS 5 SECONDS
TO LIVE.

713
00:40:43,917 --> 00:40:45,125
REPLY.

714
00:40:52,709 --> 00:40:54,709
SHE IS A VICTIM
OF WAR, CAPTAIN.

715
00:40:57,000 --> 00:40:58,417
SHE UNDERSTANDS.

716
00:41:00,500 --> 00:41:01,667
HE CALLED MY BLUFF.

717
00:41:04,083 --> 00:41:05,458
YOU'RE NOT GOING--

718
00:41:05,458 --> 00:41:08,125
THE FEDERATION DOESN'T
KILL OR MISTREAT
ITS PRISONERS.

719
00:41:08,125 --> 00:41:10,750
YOU'VE BEEN LISTENING
TO PROPAGANDA FABLES.
HOW MUCH TIME?

720
00:41:10,750 --> 00:41:12,458
8 MINUTES, 42 SECONDS.

721
00:41:15,709 --> 00:41:17,500
SO THIS WAS NO TRICK?

722
00:41:17,500 --> 00:41:19,959
IT'S THE ALIEN
THAT'S DONE THIS.

723
00:41:19,959 --> 00:41:21,500
WE'RE
IN ITS POWER,

724
00:41:21,500 --> 00:41:23,166
OUR PEOPLE
AND YOURS.

725
00:41:23,166 --> 00:41:25,875
WE ONLY WANTED TO
STOP THE FIGHTING
TO SAVE US ALL.

726
00:41:25,875 --> 00:41:27,917
WE HAVE ALWAYS
FOUGHT.

727
00:41:27,917 --> 00:41:29,917
WE MUST.

728
00:41:29,917 --> 00:41:31,917
WE ARE HUNTERS,
CAPTAIN,

729
00:41:31,917 --> 00:41:33,750
TRACKING AND TAKING
WHAT WE NEED.

730
00:41:35,792 --> 00:41:39,083
THERE ARE POOR PLANETS
IN THE KLINGON SYSTEMS.

731
00:41:39,083 --> 00:41:41,500
WE MUST PUSH OUTWARD
IF WE ARE TO SURVIVE.

732
00:41:43,125 --> 00:41:45,208
THERE'S ANOTHER WAY
TO SURVIVE--

733
00:41:45,208 --> 00:41:46,375
MUTUAL TRUST
AND HELP.

734
00:41:54,208 --> 00:41:57,291
I WILL HELP YOU NOW.

735
00:41:57,291 --> 00:41:58,625
HOW?

736
00:41:58,625 --> 00:42:01,333
I WILL TAKE YOU TO KANG.

737
00:42:01,333 --> 00:42:03,500
I WILL ADD MY VOICE
TO YOURS.

738
00:42:03,500 --> 00:42:04,625
I WOULDN'T TRUST HER,
CAPTAIN.

739
00:42:07,417 --> 00:42:10,959
WE CAN'T GET THROUGH
THE KLINGON DEFENSES
IN TIME

740
00:42:10,959 --> 00:42:11,959
UNLESS...

741
00:42:14,500 --> 00:42:15,458
SPOCK.

742
00:42:16,792 --> 00:42:18,959
INTRASHIP BEAMING.

743
00:42:18,959 --> 00:42:19,875
FROM ONE SECTION
TO ANOTHER,

744
00:42:19,875 --> 00:42:21,333
IT'S POSSIBLE?

745
00:42:21,333 --> 00:42:24,208
IT HAS RARELY BEEN DONE
BECAUSE OF THE DANGER
INVOLVED.

746
00:42:24,208 --> 00:42:26,625
PINPOINT ACCURACY
IS REQUIRED.

747
00:42:26,625 --> 00:42:30,041
IF THE TRANSPORTEE
SHOULD MATERIALIZE
INSIDE A SOLID OBJECT,

748
00:42:30,041 --> 00:42:31,625
A DECK OR A WALL--

749
00:42:31,625 --> 00:42:33,792
EVEN IF
IT COULD WORK,

750
00:42:33,792 --> 00:42:36,875
SHE MAY BE
LEADING YOU
INTO A TRAP.

751
00:42:36,875 --> 00:42:38,750
WE'RE ALL IN A TRAP.
THIS IS THE ONLY
WAY OUT.

752
00:42:38,750 --> 00:42:39,792
WE'LL GO
WITH YOU.

753
00:42:39,792 --> 00:42:43,000
NO. IT'LL START
THE FINAL BATTLE.

754
00:42:47,291 --> 00:42:48,333
I BELIEVE HER.

755
00:42:52,917 --> 00:42:55,083
PREPARE THE TRANSPORTER.
WE'LL WAIT FOR YOUR SIGNAL.

756
00:42:57,125 --> 00:43:00,250
BUT SHE CAN'T GUARANTEE
THAT KANG WILL STOP
TO LISTEN,

757
00:43:00,250 --> 00:43:02,166
RIGHT, MR. SPOCK?

758
00:43:02,166 --> 00:43:05,000
NO ONE CAN GUARANTEE
THE ACTIONS OF ANOTHER.

759
00:43:14,834 --> 00:43:17,709
YOUR AUTOMATIC SETTING
IS LAID IN, CAPTAIN.

760
00:43:17,709 --> 00:43:19,625
WHEN TRANSPORTER
IS ENERGIZED,

761
00:43:19,625 --> 00:43:22,917
YOU'LL HAVE 8 SECONDS
TO GET TO THE PADS.

762
00:43:22,917 --> 00:43:25,750
I HOPE YOUR COMPUTATIONS
ARE CORRECT, MR. SPOCK.

763
00:43:25,750 --> 00:43:28,333
YOU'LL KNOW IN
7.9 SECONDS,
CAPTAIN.

764
00:43:47,375 --> 00:43:50,083
MARA, YOU'RE ALIVE.

765
00:43:50,083 --> 00:43:51,458
AND YOU BRING US
A PRIZE.

766
00:43:51,458 --> 00:43:52,667
KANG, WAIT.

767
00:43:52,667 --> 00:43:54,500
HE'S COME ALONE,
UNARMED.

768
00:43:54,500 --> 00:43:56,458
HE MUST TALK TO YOU.

769
00:43:56,458 --> 00:43:58,417
BRAVE CAPTAIN,
WHAT ABOUT?

770
00:43:58,417 --> 00:43:59,750
NO!

771
00:43:59,750 --> 00:44:01,166
LISTEN TO HIM.

772
00:44:01,166 --> 00:44:02,750
WE ARE ALL
IN DANGER.

773
00:44:02,750 --> 00:44:05,875
MARA. BEFORE
YOU START KILLING,
GIVE ME ONE MINUTE.

774
00:44:07,083 --> 00:44:08,667
KANG, DON'T!

775
00:44:08,667 --> 00:44:10,834
WHAT HAVE THEY DONE
TO YOU, MARA?

776
00:44:10,834 --> 00:44:11,792
ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR MIND?

777
00:44:11,792 --> 00:44:12,959
WHAT HAVE THEY DONE
TO YOU?

778
00:44:18,375 --> 00:44:21,500
I SEE WHY THE HUMAN BEAST
DID NOT KILL YOU.

779
00:44:21,500 --> 00:44:24,333
THEY DIDN'T HARM ME.
LISTEN TO HIM.

780
00:44:41,208 --> 00:44:42,417
STOP!

781
00:44:43,208 --> 00:44:44,709
STOP, PLEASE!

782
00:44:49,291 --> 00:44:51,667
WITH YOUR DEATH,
WE WIN.

783
00:44:51,667 --> 00:44:52,959
NOBODY WINS.

784
00:44:52,959 --> 00:44:54,917
HAVE ANY MORE OF
YOUR MEN DIED?

785
00:44:54,917 --> 00:44:56,875
WE CAN'T BE KILLED.

786
00:44:56,875 --> 00:44:58,875
THERE'S AN ALIEN ABOARD.

787
00:44:58,875 --> 00:45:00,583
IT WANTS US ALIVE.

788
00:45:03,333 --> 00:45:06,291
NO DOUBT
YOU WILL REASSEMBLE

789
00:45:06,291 --> 00:45:08,166
AFTER I HAVE HACKED
YOU TO BITS!

790
00:45:10,208 --> 00:45:11,500
YOU FOOL.

791
00:45:48,917 --> 00:45:50,125
LOOK!

792
00:45:52,333 --> 00:45:53,792
LOOK!

793
00:45:53,792 --> 00:45:55,750
KANG, FOR THE REST
OF OUR LIVES--

794
00:45:55,750 --> 00:45:57,667
A THOUSAND LIFETIMES--

795
00:45:57,667 --> 00:45:59,458
SENSELESS VIOLENCE,

796
00:45:59,458 --> 00:46:00,834
FIGHTING,

797
00:46:00,834 --> 00:46:02,458
WHILE A-AN ALIEN

798
00:46:02,458 --> 00:46:04,250
HAS TOTAL CONTROL
OVER US.

799
00:46:20,208 --> 00:46:21,417
ALL RIGHT.

800
00:46:22,625 --> 00:46:25,125
ALL RIGHT.

801
00:46:25,125 --> 00:46:26,125
IN THE HEART.
IN THE HEAD.

802
00:46:26,125 --> 00:46:27,625
I WON'T STAY DEAD.

803
00:46:27,625 --> 00:46:29,917
NEXT TIME I'LL DO
THE SAME TO YOU.
I'LL KILL YOU.

804
00:46:29,917 --> 00:46:31,792
AND IT GOES ON AND ON,
THE GOOD OLD GAME
OF WAR,

805
00:46:31,792 --> 00:46:33,959
PAWN AGAINST PAWN!

806
00:46:33,959 --> 00:46:36,458
STOPPING THE BAD GUYS.

807
00:46:36,458 --> 00:46:39,166
WHILE SOMEWHERE
SOME...THING

808
00:46:39,166 --> 00:46:42,417
SITS BACK AND LAUGHS...

809
00:46:42,417 --> 00:46:44,375
AND STARTS IT
ALL OVER AGAIN.

810
00:46:48,000 --> 00:46:49,417
LET'S JUMP HIM.

811
00:46:49,417 --> 00:46:51,333
THOSE WHO HATE
AND FIGHT

812
00:46:51,333 --> 00:46:53,458
MUST STOP
THEMSELVES, DOCTOR.

813
00:46:53,458 --> 00:46:55,291
OTHERWISE, IT IS
NOT STOPPED.

814
00:46:55,291 --> 00:46:58,458
KANG, I AM YOUR WIFE.

815
00:46:58,458 --> 00:47:01,041
I'M A KLINGON.

816
00:47:01,041 --> 00:47:03,041
WOULD I LIE FOR THEM?

817
00:47:03,041 --> 00:47:04,667
LISTEN TO KIRK.

818
00:47:04,667 --> 00:47:06,291
HE IS TELLING THE TRUTH.

819
00:47:08,250 --> 00:47:10,417
BE A PAWN, BE A TOY,

820
00:47:10,417 --> 00:47:12,417
BE A GOOD SOLDIER THAT
NEVER QUESTIONS ORDERS.

821
00:47:26,208 --> 00:47:29,542
KLINGONS KILL
FOR THEIR OWN PURPOSES.

822
00:47:29,542 --> 00:47:31,291
ALL FIGHTING MUST END,
CAPTAIN,

823
00:47:31,291 --> 00:47:32,250
TO WEAKEN THE ALIEN

824
00:47:32,250 --> 00:47:34,375
BEFORE OUR DILITHIUM
CRYSTALS ARE GONE.

825
00:47:43,625 --> 00:47:44,792
LIEUTENANT UHURA,

826
00:47:44,792 --> 00:47:45,834
Uhura: YES, CAPTAIN?

827
00:47:45,834 --> 00:47:47,041
PUT ME ON SHIPWIDE
INTERCOM.

828
00:47:47,041 --> 00:47:48,041
Uhura: AYE, SIR.

829
00:47:48,041 --> 00:47:49,875
KANG.

830
00:47:49,875 --> 00:47:50,875
Uhura: READY, CAPTAIN.

831
00:47:53,667 --> 00:47:55,667
THIS IS CAPTAIN KIRK.

832
00:47:55,667 --> 00:47:57,166
A TRUCE IS ORDERED.

833
00:47:57,166 --> 00:47:59,083
THE FIGHTING IS OVER.

834
00:47:59,083 --> 00:48:00,208
LAY DOWN YOUR WEAPONS.

835
00:48:06,000 --> 00:48:07,333
THIS IS KANG.

836
00:48:08,709 --> 00:48:10,250
CEASE HOSTILITIES.

837
00:48:11,792 --> 00:48:12,792
DISARM.

838
00:48:22,625 --> 00:48:24,208
THE CESSATION
OF VIOLENCE

839
00:48:24,208 --> 00:48:25,750
APPEARS TO HAVE
WEAKENED IT,
CAPTAIN.

840
00:48:25,750 --> 00:48:28,333
I SUGGEST
THAT GOOD SPIRITS

841
00:48:28,333 --> 00:48:29,834
MIGHT MAKE
AN EFFECTIVE WEAPON.

842
00:48:41,125 --> 00:48:43,291
GET OFF MY SHIP!

843
00:48:43,291 --> 00:48:44,375
YOU'RE A DEAD DUCK HERE.

844
00:48:44,375 --> 00:48:46,041
YOU'RE POWERLESS.
WE KNOW ABOUT YOU.

845
00:48:46,041 --> 00:48:50,000
AND WE DON'T
WANT TO PLAY.

846
00:48:50,000 --> 00:48:52,500
MAYBE...

847
00:48:52,500 --> 00:48:53,959
MAYBE THERE ARE OTHERS
LIKE YOU AROUND.

848
00:48:53,959 --> 00:48:56,792
MAYBE YOU'VE CAUSED
A LOT OF SUFFERING,

849
00:48:56,792 --> 00:48:59,834
A LOT OF HISTORY,
BUT THAT'S ALL OVER.

850
00:48:59,834 --> 00:49:02,667
WE'LL BE ON GUARD NOW,
WE'LL BE READY FOR YOU,

851
00:49:02,667 --> 00:49:04,166
SO SHIP OUT!

852
00:49:04,166 --> 00:49:05,333
COME ON! HAUL IT!

853
00:49:05,333 --> 00:49:06,500
YEAH, OUT ALREADY.

854
00:49:08,709 --> 00:49:10,667
[KIRK AND McCOY LAUGH]

855
00:49:11,959 --> 00:49:13,625
OUT!

856
00:49:13,625 --> 00:49:16,542
WE NEED NO URGING
TO HATE HUMANS.

857
00:49:16,542 --> 00:49:17,917
BUT, FOR THE PRESENT,

858
00:49:17,917 --> 00:49:19,959
ONLY A FOOL FIGHTS
IN A BURNING HOUSE.

859
00:49:19,959 --> 00:49:20,959
OUT!

860
00:49:20,959 --> 00:49:23,166
[ALL LAUGH]
